            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1704.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> korma curry powder</strong> and cook for 10 sec</p>\r\n<p>Add the<strong> coconut stock</strong>&nbsp;with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1704.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
