            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1704.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> king prawns</strong> and<strong> ground almonds</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the prawns are cooked through and the sauce has thickened <span class=\"text-highlight\">&ndash;</span> this is your <strong>king prawn korma</strong></p>\r\n<p>Note: please ensure you cook your prawns thoroughly (until piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
